================================================================================
  MAIL ANALYZER AGENT — TECHNICAL ARCHITECTURE & COMPLETE FLOW
================================================================================

Project   : Mail Analyzer Agent
Stack     : Python 3.11 · FastMCP · LangChain · FastAPI · Gmail API · Pub/Sub
Pattern   : ReAct Supervisor Agent with MCP Tool Servers (Autonomous)
Trigger   : Gmail Pub/Sub Webhook (new email → automatic processing)

